) and 4 pairs of area porosae present. Areae A2 and A3 often near to each other, but only very exceptionally unilaterally fused (fig. 13). In one case a divided area A1 was found. Area AI not close to seta lp, ratio lp-A1:h3-A1 ranking from 1:0.75 to 1:2.6, usually about 1:1.6. All lyrifissures present in usual place, notogastral gland pore visible. Posterior border of notogaster broadly rounded.
